## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="4dfb6-102">この拡張は、IIS または WAS でホストされるサービスにのみ存在します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4dfb6-102">This extension is present only for services hosted in IIS or WAS.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4dfb6-103">サービスは、次の例に示すように、この拡張を各自の <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase> から取得することで、IIS または WAS でホストされているかどうかを決定できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4dfb6-103">Services can determine whether they are hosted in IIS or WAS by retrieving this extension from their <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>, as shown in the following example.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="4dfb6-104">サービス ホストから <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activation.VirtualPathExtension> を回復し、IIS または WAS でホストされている値を返す方法の例を次に示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4dfb6-104">The following example shows how to recover the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activation.VirtualPathExtension> from the service host and return a value that it is hosted in IIS or WAS.</span></span>  

```csharp  
bool isHosted = false;  
ServiceHostBase host = OperationContext.Current.Host;  
VirtualPathExtension vpe = host.Extentions.Find<VirtualPathExtension>();  

if( vpe != null )  
Console.WriteLine("The virtualPath of the hosted Service is  {0}", vpe.VirtualPath);  
```
